      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Great Condition & Ready to Roll \u2014 A Reliable Ride You Can Count On! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in genuinely good condition \u2014 well cared for with only the normal signs of everyday use you'd expect from a pre-owned car! The exterior presents nicely with minor cosmetic blemishes typical of its age, and the interior is clean and comfortable. Mechanically, it runs great and has been properly maintained, making it a trustworthy choice for your daily drive. If you're looking for a solid, dependable vehicle without the mint-condition price tag, this one deserves a serious look! \ud83d\udc4d",
