    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in outstanding mint condition at $47,500. The exterior is absolutely pristine \u2014 the paint is rich, deep, and completely free of scratches, scuffs, dents, or any blemishes whatsoever. Every panel gleams as if fresh from the factory, with no signs of fading or oxidation. The interior is equally immaculate: seats, carpets, dashboard, and all trim pieces are spotless and show no wear, cracking, or discoloration. Mechanically, this car is in top-tier shape \u2014 the engine runs smoothly and powerfully, all systems function perfectly, and there are no warning lights, leaks, or unusual noises. Tires have excellent tread depth, brakes are responsive and strong, and all electronics and features work flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and is as close to new as a used car can get.",
      "price": 47500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a good-condition car, and buyers can expect a reliable, well-maintained used vehicle that delivers solid everyday performance. The exterior presents nicely with only minor cosmetic blemishes \u2014 small scratches or light swirl marks consistent with normal use \u2014 but no significant dents, rust, or paint damage. The interior is clean and functional, showing modest wear on high-contact surfaces like the driver's seat and steering wheel, but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, the car runs well; all major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and suspension \u2014 are in good working order with no known issues. Service has been kept up reasonably, and the car starts reliably and drives smoothly. This is a practical, honest buy for someone seeking a dependable used vehicle without paying a premium for near-new condition.",
      "price": 35000.0,
